data.description: NEW ROOF AND NEW AC INSTALLED AND SOLAR PANELS WILL BE PAID OFF AT CLOSING ( seller wants to negotiate amount)...This house is a 4 bedroom 2.5 bath Pool home located in well established community of Ingram Trails. NO rear neighbors. Screened Pool. Kitchen has 42"wood cabinets, solid stone counters, stainless steel appliances, dining/living room combo, large family room for entertaining. This house includes solar which saves tremendously on the utility bill!... This home also comes with a pool, and plenty of space to be able to enjoy and relax. If you have a family or looking for a home with a lot of space, then you are in the right place. SOLAR PANELS have been installed which will allow new buyers to have a very economical utility bill.
